msgid "Point of Sale"
msgstr "Kassajärjestelmä"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale.rst:7
msgid ""
"Odoo **Point of Sale** is designed for managing shops and restaurants. It is "
"web-browser-based, allowing it to run on any device, and is built to "
"maintain functionality even during temporary network outages."
msgstr ""
"Odoo **Kassajärjestelmä** on suunniteltu kauppojen ja ravintoloiden "
"hallintaan. Se on verkkoselainpohjainen, minkä ansiosta se toimii millä "
"tahansa laitteella, ja se on rakennettu ylläpitämään toimivuutta jopa "
"tilapäisten verkkokatkoksien aikana."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale.rst:11
msgid ""
"Beyond traditional :doc:`store <point_of_sale/shop>` and :doc:`restaurant "
"<point_of_sale/restaurant>` settings, Odoo :abbr:`POS (Point of Sale)` also "
"supports a :doc:`self-ordering <point_of_sale/extra/self_order>` feature, "
"enabling customers to place orders and make payments using a dedicated kiosk "
"or their own mobile device."
msgstr ""
"Perinteisten :doc:`myymälä- <point_of_sale/shop>` ja :doc:`ravintola "
"<point_of_sale/restaurant>`-ympäristöjen lisäksi "
"Odoo :abbr:`Kassajärjestelmä (Point of Sale)` tukee "
"myös :doc:`itsepalvelutilaus <point_of_sale/extra/self_order>`-ominaisuutta, "
"joka mahdollistaa asiakkaiden tilausten tekemisen ja maksujen suorittamisen "
"erillisellä kioskilla tai omalla mobiililaitteellaan."

