msgstr "Cashdro-laitteen yhdistäminen Odoon tapahtuu seuraavasti:"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/cashdro.rst:55
msgid ""
":ref:`Install <general/install>` the :guilabel:`POS Cashdro Cash Machines` "
"module."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Asenna <general/install>` :guilabel:`POS Cashdro Cash Machines` "
"-moduuli."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/cashdro.rst:56
#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/terminals/dpo.rst:48
#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/terminals/tyro.rst:39
msgid ""
"Go to :menuselection:`Point of Sale --> Configuration --> Payment Methods` "
"and click :guilabel:`New`."
msgstr ""
"Siirry kohtaan :menuselection:`Kassajärjestelmä --> Asetukset --> "
"Maksutavat` ja napsauta :guilabel:`Uusi`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/cashdro.rst:58
msgid "Set the :guilabel:`Journal` field to :guilabel:`Cash`."
msgstr "Aseta :guilabel:`Päiväkirja` -kentän arvoksi :guilabel:`Käteinen`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/cashdro.rst:59
msgid "Select the relevant POS in the :guilabel:`Point of Sale` field."
msgstr ""
"Valitse asianmukainen kassajärjestelmä :guilabel:`Kassajärjestelmä` "
"-kentässä."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/cashdro.rst:60
msgid ""
"Set the :guilabel:`Integration` field to :guilabel:`Cash Machine (Cashdro)`."
msgstr ""
"Aseta :guilabel:`Integraatio` -kentän arvoksi :guilabel:`Käteisautomaatti "
"(Cashdro)`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/cashdro.rst:61
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Cashdro Settings` tab, enter the Cashdro machine's IP "
"address in the :guilabel:`Cashdro IP` field."
msgstr ""
"Anna Cashdron IP-osoite :guilabel:`Cashdro Settings` "
"-välilehdellä :guilabel:`Cashdro IP` -kenttään."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/cashdro.rst:63
msgid ""
"Enter your Cashdro user credentials in the :guilabel:`Cashdro Username` "
"and :guilabel:`Cashdro Password` fields."
msgstr ""
"Anna Cashdro-käyttäjätietosi :guilabel:`Cashdro Username`- "
"ja :guilabel:`Cashdro Password`-kenttiin."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/cashdro.rst:65
msgid "Enable :guilabel:`Cashdro Local Network Access`."
msgstr "Ota käyttöön :guilabel:`Cashdro Local Network Access`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/cashdro.rst:68
msgid ""
"It is highly recommended to use :doc:`Local Network Access <../../"
"hardware_network/pos_lna>`, as it bypasses the need for an :doc:`SSL "
"certificate <../../hardware_network/epos_ssc>`."
msgstr ""
"On erittäin suositeltavaa käyttää :doc:`Local Network Access <../../"
"hardware_network/pos_lna>` -toimintoa, koska se ohittaa :doc:`SSL-"
"sertifikaatin <../../hardware_network/epos_ssc>` tarpeen."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/cashdro.rst:72
#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/glory.rst:134
msgid ":doc:`../../payment_methods`"
msgstr ":doc:`../../payment_methods`"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/glory.rst:3
msgid "Glory"
msgstr "Glory"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/glory.rst:5
msgid ""
"**Glory** :doc:`cash machines <../cash_machines>` enable the automation of "
"cash transactions."
msgstr ""
":doc:`Käteisautomaatit <../cash_machines>` **Glory** mahdollistavat "
"käteistransaktioiden automatisoinnin."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/glory.rst:8
msgid "Odoo supports the Glory CI-5, CI-10, and CI-10X models."
msgstr "Odoo tukee Glory CI-5-, CI-10- ja CI-10X-malleja."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/glory.rst:9
msgid ""
"The Glory machine must run firmware version ISP-K05H/B v18.40 or later. Any "
"version starting with ISP-K35 is **not supported**."
msgstr ""
"Glory-koneessa on oltava laiteohjelmistoversio ISP-K05H/B v18.40 tai "
"uudempi. Mitään ISP-K35:llä alkavaa versiota **ei tueta**."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/glory.rst:12
msgid ""
"The integration with the Glory cash machine only supports basic functions, "
"such as cash transactions and cash count checks."
msgstr ""
"Integrointi Glory-käteisautomaattiin tukee vain perustoimintoja, kuten "
"käteistransaktioita ja käteislaskennan tarkistuksia."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/glory.rst:23
msgid "Cash machine settings"
msgstr "Käteisautomaatin asetukset"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/glory.rst:25
msgid ""
"Power on the cash machine, which briefly displays its IP address at the "
"bottom of the screen. Note it down for later."
msgstr ""
"Käynnistä käteisautomaatti, joka näyttää lyhyesti IP-osoitteensa näytön "
"alalaidassa. Kirjoita se ylös myöhempää käyttöä varten."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/glory.rst:29
msgid ""
"The IP address should be formatted as `###.###.#.##` (e.g., `192.168.0.25`)."
msgstr "IP-osoitteen muodon tulee olla `###.###.#.##` (esim. `192.168.0.25`)."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/glory.rst:31
msgid ""
"Navigate to the cash machine's homepage by entering its IP address as the "
"URL in `HTTPS` (e.g., `https://192.168.0.25`), and log in with your Glory "
"credentials."
msgstr ""
"Siirry käteisautomaatin kotisivulle syöttämällä sen IP-osoite URL-"
"osoitteeksi `HTTPS`-muodossa (esim. `https://192.168.0.25`) ja kirjaudu "
"sisään Glory-tunnuksillasi."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/glory.rst:33
msgid ""
"As long as the certificate is not imported, a warning page appears when "
"trying to access the machine's homepage. Bypass it by "
"clicking :guilabel:`Advanced` and then :guilabel:`Proceed to [IP address] "
"(unsafe)`."
msgstr ""
"Niin kauan kuin varmennetta ei ole tuotu, varoitussivu tulee näkyviin, kun "
"yritetään käyttää automaatin kotisivua. Ohita se "
"napsauttamalla :guilabel:`Lisäasetukset` ja sitten :guilabel:`Siirry "
"osoitteeseen [IP-osoite] (ei turvallinen)`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/glory.rst:36
msgid ""
"From the Glory homepage, go to :guilabel:`Host Configuration` and ensure "
"the :guilabel:`Network` setting is set to :guilabel:`MANUAL`, meaning the IP "
"address is static."
msgstr ""
"Siirry Glory-kotisivulta kohtaan :guilabel:`Isäntäkokoonpano` ja varmista, "
"että :guilabel:`Verkko` -asetukseksi on määritetty :guilabel:`MANUAALINEN`, "
"mikä tarkoittaa, että IP-osoite on staattinen."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/glory.rst:38
msgid ""
"Then, navigate to :guilabel:`SSL Configuration` and scroll down to "
"the :guilabel:`HTTPS Server Setting` section."
msgstr ""
"Siirry sitten kohtaan :guilabel:`SSL-määritys` ja vieritä "
"alas :guilabel:`HTTPS-palvelinasetus` -osioon."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/glory.rst:41
msgid ""
"In parallel, open the terminal and verify that *OpenSSL* is installed. Type "
"`openssl` and press enter. If installed, this command displays a `help` menu "
"listing all available OpenSSL commands. If nothing happens, `install it "
"<https://openssl-library.org/source/>`_."
msgstr ""
"Avaa rinnakkain pääte ja varmista, että *OpenSSL* on asennettu. Kirjoita "
"`openssl` ja paina Enter. Jos se on asennettu, tämä komento näyttää `help`-"
"valikon, jossa luetellaan kaikki käytettävissä olevat OpenSSL-komennot. Jos "
"mitään ei tapahdu, `asenna se <https://openssl-library.org/source/>`_."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/glory.rst:44
msgid ""
"Then, paste the following command and press `Enter` to generate and download "
"the certificate and private key. Ensure that you replace the demo IP address "
"with the cash machine’s actual IP address."
msgstr ""
"Liitä sitten seuraava komento ja paina `Enter` luodaksesi ja ladataksesi "
"varmenteen ja yksityisen avaimen. Varmista, että korvaat demon IP-osoitteen "
"käteisautomaatin todellisella IP-osoitteella."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/glory.rst:53
msgid ""
"The self-signed SSL certificate and key pair must use the same static IP "
"address as the cash machine."
msgstr ""
"Itseallekirjoitetun SSL-varmenteen ja avainparin on käytettävä samaa "
"staattista IP-osoitetta kuin kassakoneen."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/glory.rst:56
msgid ""
"Once the files are generated, from the :guilabel:`HTTPS Server Setting` "
"section, upload `cert.pem` as the :guilabel:`Certificate` and `key.pem` as "
"the :guilabel:`Private Key`."
msgstr ""
"Kun tiedostot on luotu, lataa :guilabel:`HTTPS Server Setting` -osiosta "
"`cert.pem` :guilabel:`Certificate` -kenttään ja `key.pem` :guilabel:`Private "
"Key` -kenttään."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/glory.rst:58
msgid ""
"Go to :guilabel:`WebApp Configuration` and ensure the :guilabel:`Interface` "
"setting from the :guilabel:`A: Nodejs Setting` section is set "
"to :guilabel:`Enable`."
msgstr ""
"Siirry :guilabel:`WebApp Configuration` -osioon ja varmista, "
"että :guilabel:`Interface` -asetus :guilabel:`A: Nodejs Setting` -osiossa on "
"asetettu tilaan :guilabel:`Enable`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/glory.rst:60
msgid "Then, adjust the following settings depending on the POS setup:"
msgstr "Säädä sitten seuraavat asetukset kassajärjestelmän kokoonpanon mukaan:"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/glory.rst:62
msgid ""
"If **multiple POS** are connected to the same cash machine, go "
"to :guilabel:`App Configuration`, scroll down to the :guilabel:`SOAP IF "
"Setting`, and ensure :guilabel:`Session mode` and :guilabel:`Occupy mode` "
"are both set to :guilabel:`Enable`."
msgstr ""
"Jos **useita kassajärjestelmiä** on yhdistetty samaan kassakoneeseen, "
"siirry :guilabel:`App Configuration` -osioon, vieritä alas :guilabel:`SOAP "
"IF Setting` -osioon ja varmista, että sekä :guilabel:`Session mode` "
"että :guilabel:`Occupy mode` on asetettu tilaan :guilabel:`Enable`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/glory.rst:65
msgid ""
"If **a dedicated user** has been set up on the cash machine for Odoo, which "
"is recommended, go to :guilabel:`App Configuration`, scroll down to "
"the :guilabel:`SOAP IF Setting` section, and :guilabel:`Enable` "
"the :guilabel:`User check` setting."
msgstr ""
"Jos kassakoneelle on määritetty **erillinen käyttäjä** Odoota varten, mikä "
"on suositeltavaa, siirry kohtaan :guilabel:`Sovelluksen määritys`, vieritä "
"alas :guilabel:`SOAP IF -asetus`-osioon ja :guilabel:`Ota käyttöön` "
":guilabel:`Käyttäjätarkistus`-asetus."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/glory.rst:68
msgid "Restart the cash machine to apply the new settings."
msgstr "Käynnistä kassakone uudelleen uusien asetusten ottamiseksi käyttöön."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/glory.rst:71
msgid ""
"As this setup is complex and may involve advanced knowledge of Glory "
"hardware, it is advisable to consult the Glory integration partner for "
"configuration if there is any uncertainty."
msgstr ""
"Koska tämä kokoonpano on monimutkainen ja saattaa vaatia syvällistä Glory-"
"laitteiston tuntemusta, on suositeltavaa neuvotella Glory-"
"integraatiokumppanin kanssa kokoonpanosta, jos on epävarmuutta."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/glory.rst:75
msgid "Import self-signed certificates"
msgstr "Tuo itseallekirjoitetut varmenteet"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/glory.rst:77
msgid ""
"For a long-term solution, the generated certificates must be imported into "
"the device running the POS. The import process is heavily dependent on "
"the :abbr:`OS (Operating System)` and the browser."
msgstr ""
"Pitkäaikaista ratkaisua varten luodut varmenteet on tuotava laitteeseen, "
"jolla kassajärjestelmä on käytössä. Tuontiprosessi riippuu "
"vahvasti :abbr:`käyttöjärjestelmästä` ja selaimesta."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/glory.rst:82
msgid "Windows OS"
msgstr "Windows-käyttöjärjestelmä"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/glory.rst:84
msgid ""
"Windows manages certificates, which means that self-signed certificates must "
"be imported from the certification files rather than the browser. To do so,"
msgstr ""
"Windows hallinnoi varmenteita, mikä tarkoittaa, että itseallekirjoitetut "
"varmenteet on tuotava varmennetiedostoista selaimen sijaan. Toimi "
"seuraavasti:"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/glory.rst:87
msgid ""
"Open the Windows File Explorer and locate the downloaded certification files."
msgstr "Avaa Windowsin Resurssienhallinta ja etsi ladatut varmennetiedostot."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/glory.rst:88
msgid ""
"Right-click on the certification files and select :guilabel:`Install "
"Certificate`."
msgstr ""
"Napsauta varmennetiedostoja hiiren oikealla painikkeella ja "
"valitse :guilabel:`Install Certificate`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/glory.rst:89
msgid ""
"Specify the certificate location and select the installation scope: either "
"the :guilabel:`Current User` only or all users (:guilabel:`Local Machine`). "
"Then, click :guilabel:`Next`."
msgstr ""
"Määritä varmenteen sijainti ja valitse asennuksen laajuus: joko "
"vain :guilabel:`Current User` tai kaikki käyttäjät (:guilabel:`Local "
"Machine`). Napsauta sitten :guilabel:`Next`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/glory.rst:92
msgid ""
"On the `Certificate Store` screen, tick :guilabel:`Place all certificates in "
"the following store`, click :guilabel:`Browse...`, and "
"select :guilabel:`Trusted Root Certification Authorities`."
msgstr ""
"`Certificate Store` -näytössä rastita :guilabel:`Place all certificates in "
"the following store`, napsauta :guilabel:`Browse...` ja "
"valitse :guilabel:`Trusted Root Certification Authorities`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/glory.rst:95
msgid "Click :guilabel:`Finish` and accept the pop-up security window."
msgstr ""
"Napsauta :guilabel:`Finish` ja hyväksy ponnahdusikkunan turvallisuusvaroitus."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/glory.rst:96
msgid "Restart the computer to make sure that the changes are applied."
msgstr ""
"Käynnistä tietokone uudelleen varmistaaksesi, että muutokset tulevat voimaan."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/glory.rst:98
msgid "Linux OS"
msgstr "Linux-käyttöjärjestelmä"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/glory.rst:100
msgid "When using **Google Chrome**,"
msgstr "Kun käytät **Google Chromea**:"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/glory.rst:102
#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/glory.rst:112
msgid "Open the web browser."
msgstr "Avaa selain."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/glory.rst:103
msgid ""
"Navigate to :menuselection:`Settings --> Privacy and security --> Security --"
"> Manage certificates`."
msgstr ""
"Siirry kohtaan :menuselection:`Asetukset --> Tietosuoja ja turvallisuus --> "
"Turvallisuus --> Hallitse varmenteita`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/glory.rst:105
msgid ""
"Go to the :guilabel:`Authorities` tab, click :guilabel:`Import`, and select "
"the exported certification files."
msgstr ""
"Siirry :guilabel:`Myöntäjät` -välilehdelle, napsauta :guilabel:`Tuo` ja "
"valitse viedyt varmennetiedostot."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/glory.rst:107
msgid "Accept all warnings and click :guilabel:`ok`."
msgstr "Hyväksy kaikki varoitukset ja napsauta :guilabel:`ok`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/glory.rst:108
#: ../../content/applications/sales/point_of_sale/payment_methods/cash_machines/glory.rst:117
msgid "Restart the web browser."
msgstr "Käynnistä verkkoselain uudelleen."

