"kiinteänä summana :guilabel:`Ennakkomaksun määrä` -kentässä."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/down_payment.rst:43
msgid ""
"Once all fields are filled in, click the :guilabel:`Create Draft` button. "
